nction is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/10590/', '', 'Oxymorphone, Oxycodone, Methadone, Pentazocine, Buprenorphine, Oliceridine, Morphine, Butorphanol, Fentanyl, Ibuprofen, Codeine, More', 'Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Avapritinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Ibrutinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, More', 1767369485);
